title: Action in Arabia [1944 - USA] George Sanders thriller
description:
Action in Arabia (1944 - USA)

Drama / Romance / Thriller

starring . . . . George Sanders, Virginia Bruce, Lenore Aubert
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0036579/


Aided by beautiful spy Yvonne Danesco, adventurous news reporter Michael Gordon tangles with Nazis in Damascus on the eve of World War II. The opening sequence with a map showing North Africa imitates the opening of the previous year's Casablanca including utilizing Lou Marcelle as narrator.
